skdetail:

Invocation Name: quotable quotes
des:
Ask for Quotable Quotes, and learn something witty, nuanced, or pertinent to everyday life. 

Quotable Quotes provides a fun way to hear statements that have impacted the world as we know it. 

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Quotable Quotes" or "Alexa, open Quotable Quotes" to get a quote".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
